				<div class="Separator"></div>
				<img src="/Surrey_Logo.png" alt="Surrey_Logo" id="SurreyLogo"/>
			</div>
			<div class="Subtext">
				We are the University of Surrey's AI and Data Science Society. Our mission is to create a community of students passionate about AI and Data Science.
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="Item QuickLinks">
			<p>Quick Links</p>
			<button class="collapse-btn" aria-expanded="false">
				Quick Links
				<span class="arrow">â–¼</span>
			</button>
			<div class="collapsible-content">
				<a href="#events">Events</a>
				<a href="#committee">Committee</a>
				<a href="/blog">Blog</a>
				<a href="/learning-resources">Resources</a>
				<a href="/gallery">Gallery</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="Item Contact">
			Contacts
			<div class="Icons2">
				<img src="/Whatsapp_Logo.png" alt="Whatsapp_Logo" id="WhatsappLogo"/>
				<img src="/Discord_Logo.png" alt="Discord_Logo" id="DiscordLogo"/>
				<img src="/Instagram_Logo.png" alt="Instagram_Logo" id="InstagramLogo"/>
